title: 3D Galax [AY Remake]
info:
This is a cover of 3D Galax by a 16-channel XM mod by dubmood/Razor1911 (and it's probably cover of a song by Ben Daglish).  Squeezed into 3 channels of ZX Spectrum's AY sound chip. Uses ABC stereo separation.

Soundtrack from "Logout #20" - ZX Spectrum gift-demo to Logout on his 32th birthday.
